description: Barnaby as seen wearing his new Hero suit, after having his memories manipulated. This Hero has the NEXT power "Hundred Power", which boosts his physical abilities by 100 times for five minutes (requiring an hour to recharge afterwards). He is best known for his strong kicking. He is the partner of the cyborg H-01, who is pretending to be his usual partner Wild Tiger.
name: Barnaby Brooks Jr.
